abstract: Reaction to the F.C.C.’s spectrum auction rules was not surprising. AT&T liked them. Google not so much.
snippet: Reaction to the F.C.C.’s spectrum auction rules was not surprising. AT&T liked them. Google not so much.
lead_paragraph: The Federal Communications Commission has set rules for the auctions of the UHF television spectrum. The Lede, our news blog, has some reaction:

headline.main: F.C.C. Auction Rules: Commendable or Incomplete
